snippet.title: Wings Simulator - Launch Trailer - RC Flight Simulator
snippet.description:
Wings Simulator is a next generation RC flight simulator. Perfect for learning to fly or to practice your racing skills. With up to 16 player multiplayer in racing or free flight. Wings has it all. 
https://www.wings-sim.com

If you're not sure if your computer will be able to handle Wings we have made this demo so you can see how your computer handles it with the different quality levels. http://www.kitchensink-games.com/WingsFPSTest.zip

Come and join the community in Discord
https://discord.gg/sXKfS3r

Follow us on Facebook for more updates
https://www.facebook.com/Wings-Next-generation-model-simulator-105209607726210
